### Dabblings online
This is my personal play-about page.  I will be trying things out here.  My interests that may coincide with some of yours are artificial intelligence, machine learning, reinforcement learning, supervised learning, statistical modelling, decision systems, optimization, mathematics and software engineering, also puzzles, triathlon, running, cycling, swimming, movies, philosophy, comedy and some other stuff.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
